title: John Cleese Talks To The Babylon Bee
description:
Comedy legend John Cleese, who changed comedy forever with Monty Python, sits down to talk to guys from The Babylon Bee about being at a FreedomFest conference with a bunch of gun-toting rednecks and whether monkeys are funny.
